query:
SELECT 
  id, 
  name, 
  assignedTo,
  JSON_CONTAINS(assignedTo, '1') as contains_1,
  JSON_CONTAINS(assignedTo, '2') as contains_2
FROM tasks 
WHERE assignedTo IS NOT NULL 
LIMIT 3;
